00:44:44,060 --> 00:44:45,620
 jer vas svako na svijetu

431
00:44:45,620 --> 00:44:46,420
 može provjeriti.

432
00:44:46,420 --> 00:44:47,660
 On može to ponoviti,

433
00:44:47,660 --> 00:44:48,440
 on može dokazati

434
00:44:48,440 --> 00:44:49,120
 da ste u krivu,

435
00:44:49,120 --> 00:44:50,660
 a najveća sramota je znanstvenika

436
00:44:50,660 --> 00:44:51,520
 ovo što se sad ugodilo

437
00:44:51,520 --> 00:44:53,120
 s onim klimatskim radom,

438
00:44:53,120 --> 00:44:56,000
 da vi morate svoj rad povući

439
00:44:56,000 --> 00:44:57,800
 i reći kao da nikad nije postojao.

440
00:44:57,800 --> 00:44:58,300
 Znači,

441
00:45:01,240 --> 00:45:05,120
 to je nešto što si ne možete dopustiti

442
00:45:05,120 --> 00:45:06,740
 i zato, kažem,

443
00:45:06,740 --> 00:45:08,180
