444
00:45:08,180 --> 00:45:10,420
 koji jasno kažu

445
00:45:10,420 --> 00:45:12,780
 da je hormonska kontracepcija

446
00:45:12,780 --> 00:45:14,560
 ima jako štetne učinke

447
00:45:14,560 --> 00:45:16,260
 od moždanih udara.

448
00:45:16,260 --> 00:45:18,420
 Kažem da ja sad ne nadajem sve...

449
00:45:18,420 --> 00:45:19,420
 Da ne ulazimo u to,

450
00:45:19,420 --> 00:45:21,180
 znamo da ima štetne učinke,

451
00:45:21,180 --> 00:45:22,320
 ali uopće taj,

452
00:45:22,320 --> 00:45:26,020
 da se vratim u drugi element

453
00:45:26,020 --> 00:45:29,740
 oko načina komuniciranja

454
00:45:29,740 --> 00:45:31,200
 spolnosti djeci,

455
00:45:31,240 --> 00:45:33,160
 u ovom programu.

456
00:45:33,160 --> 00:45:34,260
 Oni u stvari poručuje

457
00:45:34,260 --> 00:45:36,920
 da je jedini problem,

458
00:45:36,920 --> 00:45:38,320
 jedino ograničenje

459
00:45:38,320 --> 00:45:39,620
 je da ne ostaneš trudan.

460
00:45:39,620 --> 00:45:40,420
 To je jedino važno.

461
00:45:40,420 --> 00:45:41,680
 Dakle, vrijedi,

462
00:45:41,680 --> 00:45:43,980
 ovi koji pričaju da se brinu

463
00:45:43,980 --> 00:45:46,240
 za ravnopravnost nas žena,

464
00:45:46,240 --> 00:45:48,480
 sve svode na ženu,

465
00:45:48,480 --> 00:45:49,120
 na njezinu odgovornost,

466
00:45:49,120 --> 00:45:51,000
 odgovornost da ona ne ostane trudna

467
00:45:51,000 --> 00:45:52,300
 i to je jedina poruka.

468
00:45:52,300 --> 00:45:53,960
 Samo ti nemoj ostati trudna,

469
00:45:53,960 --> 00:45:55,120
 druga, a ako ostaneš trudna,

470
00:45:55,120 --> 00:45:56,460
 možeš pobaciti svoje dijete

471
00:45:56,460 --> 00:45:57,800
