531
00:47:45,180 --> 00:47:48,500
 da oni su već duboko ušli u sustav

532
00:47:48,500 --> 00:47:52,460
 kroz određene zakonske okvire

533
00:47:52,460 --> 00:47:54,200
 gdje oni preko udruga,

534
00:47:54,200 --> 00:47:55,600
