536
00:47:57,120 --> 00:47:58,780
 Znači, ući na način

537
00:47:58,780 --> 00:47:59,760
 da budu uvršteni

538
00:47:59,760 --> 00:48:00,820
 u školski kurikul

539
00:48:00,820 --> 00:48:03,600
 sa svojim projektom.

540
00:48:03,600 --> 00:48:05,960
 Naravno, to ovisi

541
00:48:05,960 --> 00:48:07,500
 o odluci školskog odbora

542
00:48:07,500 --> 00:48:10,280
 koji, kao što je

