549
00:48:21,180 --> 00:48:23,560
 Tako da, ta tri glasa

550
00:48:23,560 --> 00:48:24,820
 su izrazito važna.

551
00:48:25,140 --> 00:48:26,820
 3 od 7, oni imaju

552
00:48:26,820 --> 00:48:27,880
