 Još jedan koja je u školi

555
00:48:31,800 --> 00:48:33,240
 ili netko u odboru

556
00:48:33,240 --> 00:48:33,960
 koga oni onda,

557
00:48:33,960 --> 00:48:35,280
 oni imaju većinu

558
00:48:35,280 --> 00:48:36,260
 i mogu odabrat koga čini.

559
00:48:36,260 --> 00:48:37,020
 Ili da se recimo

560
