578
00:49:04,920 --> 00:49:06,380
 koje unose

579
00:49:06,380 --> 00:49:07,420
 ideološki sadržaj.

580
00:49:07,420 --> 00:49:08,160
 Nije sporno,

581
00:49:08,160 --> 00:49:08,880
 pjevanje,

582
00:49:08,880 --> 00:49:09,880
 sport,

583
00:49:09,880 --> 00:49:11,480
 paška čipka,

584
00:49:11,480 --> 00:49:12,340
 tako i sve udruge,

585
00:49:12,340 --> 00:49:13,000
 to nije sporno.

586
00:49:13,000 --> 00:49:15,220
 Mi smo isto kao udruga

587
00:49:15,220 --> 00:49:16,300
