629
00:50:06,380 --> 00:50:07,800
 4 nego 5.

630
00:50:07,800 --> 00:50:09,920
 Znači oni su uveli

631
00:50:09,920 --> 00:50:11,400
 kurikulum

632
00:50:11,400 --> 00:50:12,540
 u rijeci

633
00:50:12,540 --> 00:50:13,840
 koji se protivi

634
00:50:13,840 --> 00:50:15,000
 svim biološkim.

635
00:50:15,000 --> 00:50:16,640
 Znači oni za te svoje teze

636
00:50:16,640 --> 00:50:17,980
 gdje djete tu govore

637
00:50:17,980 --> 00:50:18,980
 da ono samo može

638
00:50:18,980 --> 00:50:20,200
 odrediti svoj

639
00:50:20,200 --> 00:50:22,040
 oni brkaju

640
00:50:22,040 --> 00:50:22,940
 stalno spol rod

641
00:50:22,940 --> 00:50:23,780
 da djete zbune.

642
00:50:23,780 --> 00:50:25,340
 Da oni sami mogu

643
00:50:25,340 --> 00:50:26,460
 odrediti svoj rod

644
00:50:26,460 --> 00:50:27,500
 da se on može

645
00:50:27,500 --> 00:50:29,120
 razlikovati od njihovog spola

646
00:50:29,120 --> 00:50:30,560
 da može biti isti

647
00:50:30,560 --> 00:50:32,180
 a da može biti nikakav.

648
00:50:32,180 --> 00:50:33,320
 Da ideologija.

649
00:50:33,320 --> 00:50:35,100
 To je ono što se djeci nameće.

