00:50:35,100 --> 00:50:36,340
 Ja se pitam

651
00:50:36,340 --> 00:50:38,240
 gdje je taj znanstveni rad

652
00:50:38,240 --> 00:50:39,480
 gdje je taj učbenik

653
00:50:39,480 --> 00:50:41,960
 koji dokazuje tu

654
00:50:41,960 --> 00:50:42,880
 znači to je

655
00:50:42,880 --> 00:50:43,660
 ono

656
00:50:43,660 --> 00:50:44,400
 i onda brkaju

657
00:50:44,400 --> 00:50:45,540
 interspolnost

658
00:50:45,540 --> 00:50:48,080
 koji je genetski poremećaj

659
00:50:48,080 --> 00:50:50,040
 sa ovom idejom

660
00:50:50,040 --> 00:50:51,640
 o nekakvom rodu

661
00:50:51,640 --> 00:50:52,940
 kao odvojujem od spola

662
00:50:52,940 --> 00:50:54,540
 i kažem to je za djete

663
00:50:54,540 --> 00:50:55,820
 užasno

664
00:50:55,820 --> 00:50:58,160
 znači ti djete tu daješ

665
00:50:58,160 --> 00:50:59,560
 dovodiš ga u nekako

666
00:50:59,560 --> 00:51:01,120
 stanje zbunjenosti

